These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee
There 2 different types of food: peach, banana
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person eating banana is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | coffee  | 7up |
| Food       | peach | banana |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | juice | fanta |
| Sport      | rowing     | baseball  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, romance
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, malaysian
1. the japanese is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the japanese is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | romance  |
| Nationality   | japanese | malaysian |

 #################################

 
