.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, indian
2 different pets are kept: ferret, bird
1. the indian is on the left or right of the australian##3
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Nationality   | australian | indian |
| Pet           | bird     | ferret  |

